import React from 'react'
import { Footer } from '../components'

export function FooterContainer() {
  return (
    <Footer>
      <Footer.Title>Questions? Contact Us.</Footer.Title>
      <Footer.Break />
      <Footer.Row>
        <Footer.Column>

        </Footer.Column>

          <Footer.Link href='#'>Ways to Watch</Footer.Link>

        </Footer.Column>
      </Footer.Row>
    </Footer>
  )
}
